    "created_at": "2018-08-23T20:33:02Z",
    "updated_at": "2018-08-23T20:33:02Z",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I'm just getting started with gRPC, Python, and proto3, and I also encountered this problem.  We were planning to leverage https://godoc.org/google.golang.org/grpc/status#Status.Details, and it looks like adding details to an error response is also a problem for gRPC _services_ written in Python.  \r\n\r\nI see that this ticket was accepted as a bug last week.  I don't know how big this bug is, but it would be helpful to understand the timeframe when we might see a fix.  That will help my team decide whether we should assume that we'll have support for Details as we start to build out our gRPC services.\r\n\r\nThanks."
