    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hello, I think I have encountered the issue if I understand your problem correctly. The service was written in Go and the client in Python. [Here is a post I did on Medium](https://medium.com/kuranda-labs-engineering/gracefully-handling-grpc-errors-in-a-go-server-python-client-setup-9805a5464692) to explain how to work around the issue. You should be able to leverage the function `trailing_metadata` of your gRPC response object in Python."
