    "created_at": "2018-09-10T15:51:59Z",
    "updated_at": "2018-09-10T15:51:59Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The automatic `status.proto` conversion from trailing metadata is not part of the gRPC package, as it needs a dependency on `protobuf`. We have plans to provide such utility API as a separate package, which would also consolidate reflection and health checking (https://github.com/grpc/grpc/issues/15830) so this would be blocked until that is resolved. In the meantime, @etiennebch's great Medium post should be helpful."
